body:
Accumulate merged HGCal, barrel ECAL/HCAL and tracker/muon/MTD pileup sim-hits in the TruthGraphAccumulator so the mixed truth graph carries pileup hit coverage. Resolve pileup hit coverage, namespace the hit-index trackId by EncodedEventId for mixed graphs, and capture tracking-detector hits only on opt-in (calo-only default). Adds the mixing customizes for pileup-aware reco. This is needed for DIGI step in production, when mixing signal with PU, both generated with the truth graph. 

To be backported to CMSSW_20_0_X

@Moanwar fyi
